 the former convective He-shell points to late\nH-ingestion events in the last days before massive stars explode as a\nsupernova.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 19:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-15"}
