 of $9.2 \\pm 0.4\n\\times 10^4\\, M_{\\odot}$ and a half-mass radius of $3.7 \\pm 0.1$ pc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2022 19:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
