isation and variability.The\nefficiency of these methodologies has been verified on known pulsars, and the\nmain limitations explained in terms of sensitivity and low-frequency spectral\nturnover of some pulsars.No candidates were confirmed to be a new pulsar.This\nnew capability will now be applied to multiple observations to accelerate\npulsar discoveries with MWA and speed up future searches with the SKA-Low.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 02:27:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
