pace-like (negative $q^2$) region of four-momentum transfer. The\nelectromagnetic form factor ratio $R_{\\rm em}\\equiv |G_E|/|G_M|$ is within the\nuncertainties close to unity. We compare our result on $|G_E|$ and $|G_M|$ to\nrecent model predictions, and the measurements in the space-like region to test\nthe analyticity of electromagnetic form factors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 07:43:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 05:36:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-30"}
