g framework called Maestro. This part\ntalks about how to schedule a workflow for execution on computing clusters and\nmake result-aware decisions while doing so. This work improves the data\nanalytics process by bringing interactivity, adaptivity and result-awareness\ninto the process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2022 08:40:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-15"}
